      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 2,
      "start": 6.99,
      "end": 11.055,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "请起勿我韩坤回老韩坤。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 3,
      "start": 11.86,
      "end": 13.62,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "那今天我们来看一看，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 4,
      "start": 14.04,
      "end": 15.835,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "最多人观看啊，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 5,
      "start": 16.65,
      "end": 18.87,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "多谢你好，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 6,
      "start": 18.87,
      "end": 24.77,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "谢你不是比我怎么才三二一要，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 7,
      "start": 26.68,
      "end": 29.35,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "我还没好准备了，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 8,
      "start": 30.46,
      "end": 30.9,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "来吧，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 9,
      "start": 31.3,
      "end": 32.46,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "做介绍一下。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 10,
      "start": 32.78,
      "end": 37.64,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "我在我我这大家好，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 11,
      "start": 37.64,
      "end": 38.58,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "我是于于谦，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 12,
      "start": 38.78,
      "end": 40.6,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "我是一虎哥啊，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 13,
      "start": 40.7,
      "end": 43.21,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "有请请声他不高。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 14,
      "start": 43.63,
      "end": 43.97,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "是的，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 15,
      "start": 43.97,
      "end": 46.7,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "二三的二掉了气，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 16,
      "start": 47.16,
      "end": 50.87,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "这人说的不好玩了哦，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 17,
      "start": 50.87,
      "end": 53.96,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "你看我年轻，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 18,
      "start": 54.02,
      "end": 55.06,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "咋不愿意走？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 19,
      "start": 56.86,
      "end": 57.6,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "阿瑞，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 20,
      "start": 57.6,
      "end": 61.26,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "接下来欢迎收看二零二五三季好声音，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 21,
      "start": 61.48,
      "end": 63.36,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "谁才是年度最佳，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 22,
      "start": 63.5,
      "end": 65.44,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "请把名字打在公屏上，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 23,
      "start": 65.66,
      "end": 68.92,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "把那一个空统通动游男有余，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 24,
      "start": 69.48,
      "end": 73.06,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "他们杀死都没口望，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 25,
      "start": 74.22,
      "end": 75.8,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "全世界都完蛋，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 26,
      "start": 76.04,
      "end": 81.78,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "变成你被困在了这片混沌留下已心实现。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 27,
      "start": 82.12,
      "end": 83.28,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "我不问怎么了？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 28,
      "start": 83.46,
      "end": 83.815,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "嗯，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 29,
      "start": 87.6,
      "end": 90.655,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "是接下来才是真正的表演，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 30,
      "start": 99.43,
      "end": 103.98,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "还会醒苦的啊啊，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 31,
      "start": 103.98,
      "end": 119.6,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "不是晚安十点了那里点音乐 location。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 32,
      "start": 119.6,
      "end": 120.0,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "tion 明，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 33,
      "start": 121.09,
      "end": 132.47,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "他们是他私然一人一次性我的出租屋里真的有很多的蟑螂。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 34,
      "start": 133.89,
      "end": 136.07,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "但是我认识的猪皮真的没有几个，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 35,
      "start": 142.99,
      "end": 149.69,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "我们绝大多数人钟情一生的活动范围可能就是在家学校公司之间挤点一线，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 36,
      "start": 150.13,
      "end": 152.93,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "而这颗星球上还有太多美好的地方。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 37,
      "start": 153.01,
      "end": 157.81,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "可能我们这辈子都不会亲自去踏足我们的视野，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 38,
      "start": 157.95,
      "end": 162.125,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "因为有他们的跋涉而得以跨越万里折叠时空？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 39,
      "start": 163.11,
      "end": 165.83,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "我们为何要建一座如此之高的大桥？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 40,
      "start": 166.31,
      "end": 168.81,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "宫崎骏的动画是一个时代的人的梦境，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 41,
      "start": 168.81,
      "end": 171.31,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "给猫咪小镇坐的地铁站的地铁。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 42,
      "start": 171.31,
      "end": 174.13,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "那么是早买早享受的一五八八朋友圈，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 43,
      "start": 174.13,
      "end": 176.45,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "每天天我去你亚过多久之后，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 44,
      "start": 176.45,
      "end": 178.33,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "我们得到了这样一件衣服啊，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 45,
      "start": 178.37,
      "end": 180.31,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "一场场酸甜苦望，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 46,
      "start": 180.43,
      "end": 182.17,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "敢问路在何方？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 47,
      "start": 182.29,
      "end": 182.39,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "哎，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 48,
      "start": 182.39,
      "end": 183.29,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "妈在来干嘛？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 49,
      "start": 183.65,
      "end": 185.35,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "那是史诗纪的一刻，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 50,
      "start": 185.77,
      "end": 186.935,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "史诗纪的一刻，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 51,
      "start": 188.01,
      "end": 189.185,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "谁在突然吹鸡，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 52,
      "start": 190.0,
      "end": 191.94,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "现在是六分五十七点三八。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 53,
      "start": 194.54,
      "end": 203.875,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "我迎这个家一二三四三选一胜万物声送给二零二五年全球总决赛冠军战队。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 54,
      "start": 205.2,
      "end": 206.655,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "他们的目光看向未来，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 55,
      "start": 208.96,
      "end": 210.085,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "就穿越回当下，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 56,
      "start": 212.96,
      "end": 215.195,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "用力感受每一个通往未来的瞬间，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 57,
      "start": 216.41,
      "end": 217.71,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "未来不知何时到来，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 58,
      "start": 218.23,
      "end": 219.335,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "但已经在路上，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 59,
      "start": 223.4,
      "end": 224.98,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "我们每个人都在互相影响，",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 60,
      "start": 225.24,
      "end": 226.58,
      "speaker": "unknown",
      "text": "成为对方经历的一部分。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 0,
      "asr_engine": "funasr-paraformer-large"
    },
    {
      "idx": 61,
